$mol_perf_dopes $mol_view
	title \Dopes
	sub /
		<= Speed $mol_view
			sub /
				<= speed \{speed} Dopes/s
		<= Start $mol_button_major
			title \@ Start
			click? <=> start? null
		<= Stop $mol_button_major
			title \@ Stop
			click? <=> stop? null
		<= Labels $mol_view
			sub <= labels /
	Label* $mol_view
		style *
			color <= label_color* \
			transform <= label_transform* \
		sub /
			\Dope
